name: No Time For Love [3]
description:
I want to remind you that in this part of the world Time has stopped for some people.

I captured a meaningful and meaningful moment in the process of research on patients in the soul disorder and traditional ways of medicine in Indonesia, I use digital techniques to mask the identity of patients and show a meaning that for them life has stopped instantly, can not see what is happening out there, can not smell the aroma of different foods that are common in people's consumption in general and can not smell their loved ones.
